            &lt;p&gt;Due to the authors, insulin is composed of two chains, A and B, crosslinked by two disulfide bridges. Therefore the sequence: Insulin = Chain B + Chain A were taken. Here, bovine insulin.&lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;/div&gt; 
